-- Bradesco Denies It’s Close to Buying Santander Brazil Unit Stake
-- B y   A n d r e   S o l i a n i
-- 2012-05-27T14:56:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-27/bradesco-denies-it-s-close-to-buying-santander-brazil-unit-stake.html
Banco Bradesco SA (BBDC4)  denied a report by
 O Globo  today saying the bank is close to buying a stake in the
Brazilian unit of rival Santander SA.  “Bradesco emphatically denies the report published in
today’s edition of  O Globo  newspaper,” the bank said in an
emailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andre Soliani in Brasilia at 
 asoliani@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sylvia Wier in  New York  at 
 swier@bloomberg.net . 